1. create command to trigger the submission of ideas (/share idea)
2. trigger state management of userstate
3. message reply to confirm they want to submit idea in inline keyboard (Yes No)
4. if yes proceeed to increment user state else reduce and resume normal user
5. if yes ask user to send and image with caption or just a message. multiple images accepted too
6. after user sends something inline keyboard to ask if thats all or send more?
store data in redis
7. if send more, allow yes to send more
8. if user done, persist data to mysql database
9. thank user and return to normal user state. 